narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: How to apply to graduate school and fellowships, how to find the right graduate program for you, who to contact in various programs, advice on how to know if graduate school is the right choice and when.

comments: not enough work time - too much lecturing/speakers

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes! I would suggest every student of color in the humanities/social sciences to apply to Mellon-Bouchet. I am so thankful for the support I have received through this program and the incredible faculty and graduate students who have helped make the program so wonderful.
Yes, MMUF has helped my research soooo much. I am a confident scholar in my field and ahead of a lot of my peers in writing and research experience.
